item.title: CVE-2023-44281|2024-08-02T19:59:51.979Z -- dell -- dell%20pair
item.description: Dell Pair Installer version prior to 1.2.1 contains an elevation of privilege vulnerability. A low privilege user with local access to the system could potentially exploit this vulnerability to delete arbitrary files and result in Denial of Service.
